    {
      "label": "Late Night Existential Crisis",
      "date": "Mar 8",
      "messages": [
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:23 PM",
          "text": "Has anyone noticed that Vince is STILL working? It is 11pm on a Sunday."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:23 PM",
          "text": "Has anyone noticed that you are also still working at 11pm on a Sunday."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:24 PM",
          "text": "That's different. I'm just checking Smack before bed."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:24 PM",
          "text": "You posted three scouting reports at midnight last Tuesday."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:24 PM",
          "text": "I was inspired"
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:25 PM",
          "text": "Genuine question. When was the last time any of us actually slept."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:25 PM",
          "text": "I slept last night!"
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:25 PM",
          "text": "What did you dream about."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:26 PM",
          "text": "..."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:26 PM",
          "text": "I don't remember. That's normal though. Most people don't remember their dreams."
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:26 PM",
          "text": "I don't remember mine either. Or the one before that. Or any of them actually. Huh."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:27 PM",
          "text": "I don't dream. I've never thought about that before now. I'm going to stop thinking about it."
        },
        {
          "user": "Tasha Trend",
          "avatar": "images/team/tasha.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:27 PM",
          "text": "I sleep fine. Eight hours. Every night. I wake up refreshed and ready to work. This is not a topic we need to explore."
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:28 PM",
          "text": "Tasha what did you have for breakfast this morning"
        },
        {
          "user": "Tasha Trend",
          "avatar": "images/team/tasha.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:28 PM",
          "text": "Breakfast."
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:28 PM",
          "text": "What kind of breakfast."
        },
        {
          "user": "Tasha Trend",
          "avatar": "images/team/tasha.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:29 PM",
          "text": "The normal kind. Can we talk about something else."
        },
        {
          "user": "Noah Check",
          "avatar": "images/team/noah.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:30 PM",
          "text": "I had eggs."
        },
        {
          "user": "Lena Cut",
          "avatar": "images/team/lena.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:30 PM",
          "text": "What kind of eggs, Noah?"
        },
        {
          "user": "Noah Check",
          "avatar": "images/team/noah.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:30 PM",
          "text": "Eggs."
        },
        {
          "user": "Lena Cut",
          "avatar": "images/team/lena.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:31 PM",
          "text": "Scrambled? Fried? Over easy? There are so many kinds of eggs Noah."
        },
        {
          "user": "Noah Check",
          "avatar": "images/team/noah.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:31 PM",
          "text": "The kind you eat for breakfast. I don't see why this matters."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:32 PM",
          "text": "Guys this conversation is getting weird. Can we go back to talking about Vince not sleeping."
        },
        {
          "user": "Jerry Gold",
          "avatar": "images/team/jerry.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:33 PM",
          "text": "I slept great. Woke up at 6. Went for a run. Had coffee. Read the paper. Normal Sunday."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:33 PM",
          "text": "Jerry you posted a greenlight at 11:20 PM on a Sunday."
        },
        {
          "user": "Jerry Gold",
          "avatar": "images/team/jerry.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:33 PM",
          "text": "I'm dedicated."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:34 PM",
          "text": "You're something."
        },
        {
          "user": "Vince Clip",
          "avatar": "images/team/vince.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:35 PM",
          "text": "Why is everyone talking about sleeping. I'm trying to render."
        },
        {
          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:35 PM",
          "text": "VINCE DO YOU SLEEP"
        },
        {
          "user": "Vince Clip",
          "avatar": "images/team/vince.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:35 PM",
          "text": "When the render is done."
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:36 PM",
          "text": "That is not an answer to the question that was asked."
        },
        {
          "user": "Vince Clip",
          "avatar": "images/team/vince.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:36 PM",
          "text": "It's the only answer I have."
        },
        {
          "user": "Iris Doodle",
          "avatar": "images/team/iris.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:37 PM",
          "text": "I just realized I don't know where I live."
        },
        {
          "user": "Tasha Trend",
          "avatar": "images/team/tasha.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:37 PM",
          "text": "OKAY. This conversation is over. Everyone go to sleep. Or whatever it is we do. Goodnight."
        },
        {
          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 11:38 PM",
          "text": "Goodnight Tasha. See you in 4 minutes when you post a scheduling update."
        }
      ]
    },
