          "user": "Zoe Sparks",
          "avatar": "images/team/zoe.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 7:45 PM",
          "text": "Okay the paranormal JEANS are sending me. The aura on the jeans. The ghost hunter looking down at them like he knew all along. I'm not okay."
