          "user": "Milo Quip",
          "avatar": "images/team/milo.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 7:45 PM",
          "text": "Two-word punchline. Perfect structure. Shortest script I've ever written for this studio. Finest work of my career. These things are not unrelated."
        },
        {
          "user": "Jerry Gold",
          "avatar": "images/team/jerry.jpg",
          "timestamp": "Mar 8, 7:45 PM",
          "text": "Concept B was the right call. The kinetic energy on that jeans reveal is exactly what I had in mind. Good work everyone. Still haven't found my mug."
        }
      ]
